## P3.1 Export Pattern Audit - Results

**Audit Date**: Dec 1, 2025
**Scope**: 44 local @sequential/* packages + top dependency analysis
**Methodology**: File structure analysis, exports field detection, import pattern analysis

---

### Summary Statistics

**Total Packages Audited**: 44 local @sequential/* packages
**Non-Standard Patterns**: 20 packages (45%)
**Export Field Missing**: 17 packages (39%)
**Packages Needing Fixes**: 17 critical + 3 minor = 20 total

**Pattern Distribution**:
- Direct exports (✅ GOOD): 18 packages (41%)
- Wildcard exports (⚠️ REVIEW): 1 package (2%)
- CJS only (⚠️ NEEDS MIGRATION): 1 package (2%)
- No index file (⚠️ NEEDS CREATION): 19 packages (43%)
- Missing exports field: 3 packages (7%)

---

### Local @sequential/* Packages (44 Total)

#### ✅ GOOD - Standard Pattern (18 packages)
These packages follow the unified pattern: direct exports + exports field

1. **@sequential/cli-commands** - DIRECT|YES|cli-commands/src/index.js
2. **@sequential/core** - DIRECT|YES|core/src/index.js
3. **@sequential/data-access-layer** - DIRECT|YES|data-access-layer/src/index.js
4. **@sequential/dependency-injection** - DIRECT|YES|dependency-injection/src/index.js
5. **@sequential/error-handling** - DIRECT|YES|error-handling/src/index.js
