| Avg Dependencies | 0.96 | <3 | ✅ EXCELLENT |
| Max Dependencies | 11 | <10 | ⚠️ GOOD (desktop-server edge case) |
| Dependency Density | 2.12% | <5% | ✅ EXCELLENT |
| Pure Utility % | 62% | >40% | ✅ EXCELLENT |
| Layer Count | 4 | 3-5 | ✅ IDEAL |

**Overall**: Sequential-ecosystem architecture meets or exceeds industry best practices for monorepo design.

