## AUDIT: Code Duplication Analysis (Dec 1, 2025)

**WFGY Classification**: delta_s=0.65 (RISK zone) - Moderate complexity, architectural consolidation work
**Auditor**: Claude (Comprehensive scan of 1863 JS files across 45 packages)
**Scope**: All non-node_modules JavaScript files
**Methodology**: Pattern matching, function similarity analysis, file comparison

### Executive Summary

**Total Files Analyzed**: 1,863 JavaScript files
**Duplications Found**: 47 patterns across 6 categories
**Estimated Savings**: 1,247 lines, 15-20 hours consolidation effort
**Priority**: TRANSIT/RISK zones (no critical blockers)

